{"tid":1108503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聖母院大火：開雲集團CEO　捐1億歐元助重建","createTime":"2019-04-16T04:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T04:15:48.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b430341152d138b331b61e0a8944750116374aa","tid":1108503,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T04:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190416/photo/bkn-20190416091200884-0416_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190416112524\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190416%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190416091200884-0416_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190416112524&h=d3ce2428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n皮諾宣布捐出巨額資金，協助聖母院日後的重建工程。<br />\n<br />\n法國巴黎聖母院的大火，令全國人民心碎不已。法國總統馬克龍已將聖母院大火列為國家緊急情況，表示要重建聖母院，呼籲國際社會協助。法國億萬富豪弗朗索瓦‧亨利‧皮諾立刻宣布捐出1億歐元（約8.87億港元），協助日後的重建工程。 <br />\n<br />\n據福布斯估計，皮諾資產總值約150億美元（約1170億港元）。他任職開雲集團主席，旗下包括Gucci及聖羅蘭（YSL）等國際時尚品牌。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190416/mobile/bkn-20190416091200884-0416_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190416%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190416091200884-0416_00912_001.html&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=e3608445\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190416/mobile/bkn-20190416091200884-0416_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9e47a727f7d87aceeb02c37d08edbc27eb1a2a20","tid":1108503,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}